<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Greatsword - Untamed Weapons</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<nav class="nav">
			<div class="container">
				<a href="/" class="logo">UNTAMED</a>
				<div class="nav-links">
					<a href="/rules">Rules</a>
					<a href="/quick-reference">Quick Reference</a>
					<a href="/character">Characters</a>
					<a href="/bestiary">Bestiary</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<main>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="breadcrumb">
					<a href="/character">‚Üê Back to Character Creation</a>
				</div>

				<header class="page-header">
					<div class="weapon-icon">‚öîÔ∏è</div>
					<h1>Greatsword</h1>
					<p class="subtitle">Heavy Burst / Part Breaker</p>
					<div class="stat-badges">
						<span class="stat-badge">+1 STR</span>
						<span class="stat-badge">+1 CON</span>
					</div>
				</header>

				<article class="content">
					<!-- Overview -->
					<section class="weapon-section">
						<h2>Overview</h2>
						<p>The Greatsword is a hulking weapon designed for hunters who prioritize raw strength and devastating attacks. While capable of dealing massive damage, wielding the Greatsword requires precision and timing, as it leaves the user vulnerable if misused. Its techniques revolve around heavy, sweeping strikes that punish enemies but demand stamina and focus.</p>
					</section>

					<!-- Weapon Attributes -->
					<section class="weapon-section">
						<h2>Weapon Attributes</h2>
						<div class="attributes-grid">
							<div class="attribute-card">
								<h3>Tags</h3>
								<ul>
									<li>Heavy</li>
									<li>Two-Handed</li>
									<li>Parry (reaction)</li>
									<li>Commitment (some moves)</li>
									<li>Wind-up (Executioner)</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
							<div class="attribute-card">
								<h3>Save DC</h3>
								<p class="formula">10 + STR modifier + proficiency (if trained)</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Damage Dice -->
					<section class="weapon-section">
						<h2>Damage Dice per Tier</h2>
						<table class="damage-table">
							<thead>
								<tr>
									<th>Tier</th>
									<th>Damage Dice</th>
								</tr>
							</thead>
							<tbody>
								<tr>
									<td>Tier 1</td>
									<td>1d12 + STR Modifier</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>Tier 2</td>
									<td>2d6 + STR Modifier</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>Tier 3</td>
									<td>2d8 + STR Modifier</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>Tier 4</td>
									<td>3d6 + STR Modifier</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>Tier 5</td>
									<td>3d8 + STR Modifier</td>
								</tr>
							</tbody>
						</table>
					</section>

					<!-- Core Mechanic -->
					<section class="weapon-section highlight">
						<h2>Core Mechanic ‚Äî Momentum</h2>
						<p>You build charge by landing hits and cash it out through stronger crit threat and baseline damage‚Äîno micro-spend hoops.</p>

						<div class="mechanic-details">
							<h3>How It Works</h3>
							<ul>
								<li><strong>Gain:</strong> +1 Momentum each time you hit with a Greatsword attack.</li>
								<li><strong>Lose all:</strong> if you miss, Dodge, switch targets, or become Stunned/Prone.</li>
								<li><strong>Cap:</strong> Maximum 3 Momentum</li>
							</ul>

							<h3>Banked Bonuses (don't spend)</h3>
							<div class="momentum-tiers">
								<div class="momentum-tier">
									<h4>1 Momentum</h4>
									<p>+1 flat damage on Greatsword attacks</p>
								</div>
								<div class="momentum-tier">
									<h4>2 Momentum</h4>
									<p>+2 flat damage total and Expanded Crit +1 (crit on 19‚Äì20)</p>
								</div>
								<div class="momentum-tier">
									<h4>3 Momentum</h4>
									<p>+3 flat damage total, Expanded Crit +2 (crit on 18‚Äì20). Gain 1 power die on all attacks.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Techniques -->
					<section class="weapon-section">
						<h2>Techniques by Tier</h2>

						<!-- T1 -->
						<div class="technique-card">
							<div class="technique-header">
								<h3>T1 ‚Äî Cleave</h3>
								<div class="technique-cost">2 Stamina ‚Ä¢ Commitment</div>
							</div>
							<p>A massive, overhand strike.</p>
							<p><strong>Attack:</strong> Base Greatsword damage + STR Modifier, advantage on the roll.</p>
							<p><strong>Drawback:</strong> You are Exposed until the end of your next turn (attacks vs you have advantage).</p>
							<p><strong>Momentum kicker:</strong> If you had 0 Momentum when you declare Cleave and it hits, gain +2 Momentum instead of +1.</p>
						</div>

						<!-- T2 -->
						<div class="technique-card">
							<div class="technique-header">
								<h3>T2 ‚Äî Blade Wave</h3>
								<div class="technique-cost">2 Stamina ‚Ä¢ Commitment, Rooting</div>
							</div>
							<p>A sweeping energy wave that strikes all enemies in an arc.</p>
							<p><strong>Range:</strong> 15-ft arc originating from you</p>
							<p><strong>Attack:</strong> Make one STR-based attack roll vs AR and apply it to all creatures in the arc. On hit: Base Greatsword damage + STR.</p>
							<p><strong>Save on Hit:</strong> Each hit target makes a STR or DEX save (DC = 10 + your STR mod + proficiency). Fail: Gains Staggered until the end of its next turn.</p>
							<div class="momentum-bonus">
								<strong>Momentum Synergy:</strong>
								<ul>
									<li>M1: Range becomes 20 ft.</li>
									<li>M2: The wave ignores half cover.</li>
									<li>M3: Add +1 Power Die. After resolving, leave a Crescent Scar along the arc: those squares are difficult terrain until the start of your next turn.</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>

						<!-- T3 -->
						<div class="technique-card">
							<div class="technique-header">
								<h3>T3 ‚Äî Titan's Guard</h3>
								<div class="technique-cost">2 Stamina ‚Ä¢ Reaction, Guard, Rooting, Parry</div>
							</div>
							<p>The only defensive move available to a Greatsword user. You plant your weapon in the ground, bracing for an incoming attack before striking back.</p>
							<p><strong>Timing:</strong> Reaction (declare after you're targeted, before damage is rolled)</p>
							<p><strong>Effect (until start of your next turn):</strong></p>
							<ul>
								<li>Halve all damage you take.</li>
								<li>If an enemy successfully hits you during this window, you may immediately make one free Basic Greatsword attack against that attacker (0 Stamina).</li>
								<li>If that counter hits, it grants +1 Momentum as usual (respecting the cap).</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<!-- T4 -->
						<div class="technique-card">
							<div class="technique-header">
								<h3>T4 ‚Äî Tremor Strike</h3>
								<div class="technique-cost">3 Stamina ‚Ä¢ Commitment, AoE</div>
							</div>
							<p>A ground-shaking downward slam that damages everything nearby and leaves a crater.</p>
							<p><strong>Attack:</strong> Melee strike vs one target: 3d12 + STR Modifier on hit.</p>
							<p><strong>Shockwave:</strong> All creatures within 10 ft of the impact spot must make a DEX save (DC = 10 + STR mod + proficiency):</p>
							<ul>
								<li>Fail: knocked Prone.</li>
								<li>Success: no prone.</li>
							</ul>
							<p><strong>Momentum 3:</strong> Your main hit also gains +1 Power Die (in addition to your global +1 Power Die from holding 3 Momentum).</p>
						</div>

						<!-- T5 -->
						<div class="technique-card">
							<div class="technique-header">
								<h3>T5 ‚Äî Executioner's Strike</h3>
								<div class="technique-cost">4 Stamina ‚Ä¢ Wind-Up, Commitment, Rooting</div>
							</div>
							<p>A fully charged, all-or-nothing finisher.</p>
							<p><strong>Charge (Turn 1):</strong> You spend your Action to charge. You are Rooted and have disadvantage on DEX saves until the attack resolves.</p>
							<p><strong>Execution (Turn 2):</strong> Make a single attack: (Base Greatsword damage + STR Modifier) √ó 2 on hit.</p>
							<p><strong>Crit:</strong> If the attack crits (use your current crit range; 18‚Äì20 at Momentum 3), it deals √ó4 damage instead.</p>
							<p><strong>On hit:</strong> target becomes Staggered (loses its next turn) ‚Äî subject to your Escalating Resistance rule.</p>
							<div class="momentum-bonus">
								<strong>Momentum interactions:</strong>
								<ul>
									<li>If you start the charge at Momentum 3, the execution attack is made with advantage and gains +1 Power Die on hit.</li>
									<li>If you drop Momentum before resolving, you lose those bonuses.</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Playstyle -->
					<section class="weapon-section playstyle">
						<h2>Weapon Playstyle</h2>
						<div class="playstyle-grid">
							<div class="playstyle-card strengths">
								<h3>üí™ Strengths</h3>
								<ul>
									<li>Massive burst potential if you play smart and build Momentum</li>
									<li>Devastating critical and AoE attacks</li>
									<li>Can solo stagger or eliminate monsters with well-timed finishers</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
							<div class="playstyle-card weaknesses">
								<h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Weaknesses</h3>
								<ul>
									<li>Vulnerable when whiffing or interrupted</li>
									<li>Stamina-hungry without Momentum</li>
									<li>Momentum loss punishes sloppy play</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>
				</article>
			</div>
		</main>

		<style>
			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			:root {
				--forest-dark: #1a2e1a;
				--forest-green: #2d5016;
				--moss-green: #4a7c2f;
				--leaf-green: #6b9d3a;
				--amber: #d4a257;
				--earth-brown: #5c4033;
				--cream: #f5f1e8;
				--text-light: #e8e4d8;
			}

			body {
				font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				color: var(--text-light);
				line-height: 1.7;
				min-height: 100vh;
			}

			.container {
				max-width: 1000px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 0 2rem;
			}

			/* Navigation */
			.nav {
				background: var(--forest-green);
				border-bottom: 2px solid var(--amber);
				padding: 1rem 0;
				position: sticky;
				top: 0;
				z-index: 100;
			}

			.nav .container {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				max-width: 1200px;
			}

			.logo {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				font-weight: 900;
				color: var(--amber);
				text-decoration: none;
				letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
			}

			.nav-links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 2rem;
			}

			.nav-links a {
				color: var(--cream);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
				transition: color 0.3s;
			}

			.nav-links a:hover {
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Breadcrumb */
			.breadcrumb {
				padding: 2rem 0 1rem;
			}

			.breadcrumb a {
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.breadcrumb a:hover {
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Page Header */
			.page-header {
				padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
				text-align: center;
				border-bottom: 2px solid var(--amber);
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}

			.weapon-icon {
				font-size: 5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.page-header h1 {
				font-size: 3rem;
				color: var(--amber);
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.subtitle {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				font-style: italic;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.stat-badges {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				gap: 1rem;
			}

			.stat-badge {
				padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
				background: var(--moss-green);
				color: var(--amber);
				border-radius: 8px;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 1.1rem;
			}

			/* Content */
			.content {
				padding-bottom: 4rem;
			}

			.weapon-section {
				background: var(--forest-green);
				padding: 2rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				border: 2px solid var(--earth-brown);
			}

			.weapon-section.highlight {
				border-color: var(--amber);
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--forest-green) 0%, var(--moss-green) 100%);
			}

			.weapon-section h2 {
				color: var(--amber);
				font-size: 2rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.weapon-section h3 {
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
			}

			.weapon-section p {
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.weapon-section ul {
				margin-left: 1.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.weapon-section li {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			/* Attributes Grid */
			.attributes-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}

			.attribute-card {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 2px solid var(--earth-brown);
			}

			.attribute-card h3 {
				color: var(--amber);
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.attribute-card ul {
				list-style: none;
				margin: 0;
			}

			.attribute-card li {
				padding-left: 1.5rem;
				position: relative;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.attribute-card li:before {
				content: "‚ñ∏";
				position: absolute;
				left: 0;
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			.formula {
				background: var(--moss-green);
				padding: 1rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				border-left: 4px solid var(--amber);
				font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--amber);
				text-align: center;
			}

			/* Damage Table */
			.damage-table {
				width: 100%;
				border-collapse: collapse;
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				border-radius: 8px;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.damage-table th,
			.damage-table td {
				padding: 1rem;
				text-align: left;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--earth-brown);
			}

			.damage-table th {
				background: var(--moss-green);
				color: var(--amber);
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			.damage-table tr:last-child td {
				border-bottom: none;
			}

			/* Mechanic Details */
			.mechanic-details h3 {
				margin-top: 1.5rem;
			}

			.momentum-tiers {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
				gap: 1rem;
				margin-top: 1rem;
			}

			.momentum-tier {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				border-left: 4px solid var(--amber);
			}

			.momentum-tier h4 {
				color: var(--amber);
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.momentum-tier p {
				margin: 0;
			}

			/* Technique Cards */
			.technique-card {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 2rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 2px solid var(--amber);
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.technique-header {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				padding-bottom: 1rem;
				border-bottom: 2px solid var(--earth-brown);
			}

			.technique-header h3 {
				color: var(--amber);
				font-size: 1.75rem;
				margin: 0;
			}

			.technique-cost {
				background: var(--moss-green);
				padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
				border-radius: 6px;
				color: var(--amber);
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
			}

			.momentum-bonus {
				background: var(--moss-green);
				padding: 1rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				margin-top: 1rem;
			}

			.momentum-bonus strong {
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			.momentum-bonus ul {
				margin-top: 0.5rem;
			}

			/* Playstyle */
			.playstyle-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}

			.playstyle-card {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 2rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 2px solid var(--earth-brown);
			}

			.playstyle-card.strengths {
				border-color: var(--leaf-green);
			}

			.playstyle-card.weaknesses {
				border-color: #c74440;
			}

			.playstyle-card h3 {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.playstyle-card ul {
				list-style: none;
				margin: 0;
			}

			.playstyle-card li {
				padding-left: 1.5rem;
				position: relative;
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
			}

			.playstyle-card li:before {
				content: "‚ñ∏";
				position: absolute;
				left: 0;
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Responsive */
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.nav .container {
					flex-direction: column;
					gap: 1rem;
				}

				.nav-links {
					gap: 1rem;
					flex-wrap: wrap;
					justify-content: center;
				}

				.page-header h1 {
					font-size: 2rem;
				}

				.weapon-section {
					padding: 1.5rem;
				}

				.technique-header {
					flex-direction: column;
					align-items: flex-start;
					gap: 1rem;
				}
			}

			/* Smooth Scrolling */
			html {
				scroll-behavior: smooth;
			}
		</style>
	</body>
</html>
